name: BAD KITTY Comicettes
description:
Ruin your eye sight and laugh until you pee. Convinced yet? No? Ok, I'll explain further.

Comicettes are a miniature comic book that fit into a cigarette box and comes with a magnify glass. Included in every box is a cheap plastic toy all because I loved Cracker Jacks when I was a kid. Oh you once were a kid too? We have so much in common.

Bad Kitty is a black comedy comic strip starring Kitty, who is bad. There are seventy something strips in this book, I'm too lazy to count that high to figure out the correct number. This product would make a bad gift to someone who enjoys hobbies like acting boring or being offended by stuff.

Thank you for reading this, now please buy the product.

You're welcome.

name: UNDERCULTURE Comicette
description:
You know the excitement of seeing a large picture very very small? Well you'll surely experience that with the UNDERCULTURE Comicette. Zero words in this miniature book. ZERO! That means no reading! There are far more words in this description of UNDERCULTURE Comicettes than there are words in UNDERCULTURE Comicette. 

Every UNDERCULTURE Comicette contains a Comicette Book, box, horrible plastic toy, a magnify glass, and a ball point pen cap because I have a lot of ball point pen caps. Why do they make pen caps still? I'll ask Mr. Google about that later. So um, thank you for reading.  Give me money now?

name: STICK FIGURE Comicette
description:
This Comicette has the most original comic strip character ever known, like ever. What makes this Stick Figure comic so amazing? Text your answer now to *767 and enter to win a contest that you won't win. No, don't text to that number. It was a joke. Moving on.

Every Stick Figure Comicette comes with a Comicette, magnify glass, red tinsel, box, and dice for no reason. You too can own one, if you dare. And I dare you. Double Dare! PHYSICAL CHALLENGE! Oh early 90's Nickelodeon, you have warped my mind forever. Every Comicette is made with 100% dead tree.

name: BAD KITTY Comic Strip Book
description: Owning this book not only makes you cool, but it also makes you look well read. I recommend enjoying this book while wearing your best smoking jacket and sipping your very expensive Scotch. Not only does this book contain the same Bad Kitty comic strips as in the Comicette, but it also features the same amount to spelling errors. And remember, if you buy two Bad Kitty Comic Strip Books, you can read one and throw the other into the garbage can.

name: TRUE STORIES (Of My Life) a comic book
description: I have had a lot of adventures in my life and this book proves it. 100% farce and poorly executed drawings make up this made up comic book. Why would you buy this? Because I'm a very critical person and I enjoyed reading it, making it critically acclaimed.
